        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 7. A–E. Adeonella assegai n. sp. (SAMC-A028960) A. Autozooids at the growing edge (scale bar = 0.2 mm, magnified x75). B. Frontal view of autozooids near the margin (scale bar = 0.2 mm, magnified x75). C. Close-up of two zooids (scale bar = 0.2 mm, magnified x100). D. Close-up of the secondary orifice, paired frontal avicularia and spiramen (scale bar = 0.1 mm, magnified x200). E. Dimorphic brooding zooids at the branch margin (scale bar = 0.4 mm, magnified x50)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4397392/files/figure.png" .

